nodes.name: intro_q0_Introduction
nodes.HTML: Introduction: Hello, I would like to ask for your permission to interview you and your family on behalf of a program which is aiming to improve girl’s education in lots of countries around the world.  We would like to ask you some questions about your family background, any education programmes your daughters are a part of and how they feel about education. If you chose to take part, the results will not be shared with your school and do not affect school grades. We will record the answers to use them in our research but we will not mention you by name or share your personal details with anybody outside of our team. Is that acceptable and do you agree to take part in the interview to help improve girl’s education?
